	<h3>Ray Butler :</h3>
	<p class="date">04 Apr 2015 6:12:13am</p>
	<p class="comment">I wrote a 70,000 word dramatization of the events around the life and death of Jesus, it is probably completely alien to how most people imagine how things went down but personally I believe my depiction is not only valid but very likely.<br /><br />However I do not claim to have full knowledge of how things were in that society, cultural practices, political structures, figures of influence, etc. So I am sure people who actually have facts on it will find a lot of holes in my account.<br /><br />Besides that I think my story raises a lot of interesting angles that may be worth exploring if people were so inclined. For some reason I am unable to enter my email address but I have posted on this site before and if you are curious about my work and can find my email address I will happily return it as an attachment for your indulgence.</p>
	
